ched by the jinn, who\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15740,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/20\/fear-muslims-kill-for-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":37255,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Greed: The Prophet fears Muslims will fight for wealth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Verily, I am not afraid that you will commit idolatry, rather I am afraid you will compete with each other for the world.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4042, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2296 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32182,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/avoid-seven-mortal-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":37255,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Avoid seven major sins, idolatry, killing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cStay away from seven mortal sins.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are they?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIdolatry with Allah, occult magic, killing a soul that Allah has sanctified except for a just cause, consuming usury, usurping\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":391,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/20\/rights-allah-tawheed\/","url_meta":{"origin":37255,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Monotheism: Rights of Allah upon His servants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 20, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu'adh bin Jabal reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"O Mu'adh, do you know what the right of Allah is upon His servants?\" I said, \"Allah and His Messenger know best.\" The Prophet said, \"To worship Him alone and to associate none in worship with Him.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2901,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/16\/bidah-innovation-jews-christians\/","url_meta":{"origin":37255,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Bid&#8217;ah: Muslims make same mistakes as previous nations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou will surely follow the path of those before you, step by step and inch by inch. If they entered a lizard hole, you would follow.\u201d We said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, do you mean\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7564,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/major-sins-idolatry-murder\/","url_meta":{"origin":37255,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Major sins are idolatry, infanticide, adultery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the greatest sin?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTo set up a partner alongside Allah, even though He alone created you.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTo kill your child, fearing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37255","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=37255"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37255\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=37255"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyha